data.title: Old Manchester Museum – Manchester Historical Society
data.meta_description: The Manchester Historical Society's Old Manchester Museum is located at 126 Cedar Street, near Washington School.
data.text:
The Manchester Historical Society’s Old Manchester Museum is located at 126 Cedar Street, near Washington School. Call for a tour 860-647-9983.

The Old Manchester Museum at 126 Cedar Street, is usually open the first Saturday of the month, from 10:00 a.m. to 2:00 p.m. May through December except holidays.
